net.hudup.core.logistic

Class MinMax

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.logistic.Dual
      • net.hudup.core.logistic.MinMax
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MinMax
extends Dual
    This utility class contains a minimum value and maximum value. It inherits from the Dual class. The minimum value and the maximum value are represented by the variable Dual.one and the variable Dual.other of its parent class Dual, respectively.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
